          SHORTCUTS
          _________


Auskommentieren:          cmd + shift + 7
jumping between files:    option + 1 or 2 and so on
searchbar:                cmd + p
moving line:              option + arrow up or down
mark inline:              shift + option + left/right arrows
mark up or down           shift + up/down arrow





          EXTENSIONS
          __________


change words all at ones: ctrl + d   ctrl + shift + l        :  Multiple cursor case preserve


• Thunder Client  -> does the same like postman, just much faster and in VSCode

                                                                                https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hSEZJqacL0c&ab_channel=DigitalOcean
    Making a POST request -> http://localhost:1337/api/auth/local/register
    
    Making a GET request for login -> http://localhost:1337/api/auth/local



• DONT use Prettier -> i had big issues just because of autoformating

*** DONT use Prettier -> i had big issues just because of autoformating ***
          USING '' instead of "" with prettier
          ____________________________________
          
          
1. create a file: .prettierrc
2. {
    "singleQuote": true,
    "arrowParens": "avoid"              // for arrow functions
   }



